<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About MPI | Magura Polytechnic Institute</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/about.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/locomotive-scroll@3.5.4/dist/locomotive-scroll.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.2/gsap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.2/ScrollTrigger.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body data-scroll-container>

    <div class="smooth-wrapper" data-scroll data-scroll-speed="0.1">
        <section class="panel hero" id="section1">
            <div class="overlay"></div>
            <div class="content glass reveal-up">
                <span class="badge">Est. 2008</span>
                <h1>Magura Polytechnic <br><span class="accent-text">Institute</span></h1>
                <p>Developing skilled human resources for the global engineering landscape.</p>
                <div class="btn-group">
                    <button class="btn-primary main-btn">Our Story</button>
                    <button class="btn-secondary main-btn">Explore Campus</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="scroll-hint">SCROLL <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        </section>

        <section class="panel stats" id="section2">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title reveal-side">Institutional Excellence</h2>
                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <h3 class="counter" data-target="1800">0</h3>
                        <p>Total Students</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <h3 class="counter" data-target="45">0</h3>
                        <p>Expert Instructors</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <h3 class="counter" data-target="12">0</h3>
                        <p>Tech Labs</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="panel history-section" id="section2">
    <div class="history-container">
        <div class="side-text reveal-side">
            <h2 class="section-heading">Heritage of <span class="accent-text">Excellence</span></h2>
            <p>Founded in 2008 under the Directorate of Technical Education, MPI has grown from a small technical school into a beacon of engineering in the Khulna Division.</p>
            <div class="milestone">
                <div class="year">2008</div>
                <div class="event">Foundation laid to bridge the technical gap in Magura district.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="milestone">
                <div class="year">2024</div>
                <div class="event">Now hosting 1,800+ students across 4 specialized technologies.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="side-image reveal-up">
            <div class="image-stack">
                <div class="main-img" style="background-image: url('/images/frontOfcollege.jpg')"></div>
                <div class="sub-img" style="background-image: url('/images/consol.log.jpg')"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="panel academic-section" id="section3">
    <div class="academic-grid">
        <div class="academic-grid">
            <div class="info-card reveal-card">
                <i class="fas fa-laptop-code"></i>
                <h3>Computer Technology</h3>
                <p>Advanced software engineering, networking, and cyber security protocols.</p>
                <button class="btn-sm-stylish">View Syllabus</button>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card reveal-card">
                <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i>
                <h3>Electrical Technology</h3>
                <p>Power plant engineering, industrial wiring, and electrical machine design.</p>
                <button class="btn-sm-stylish">View Syllabus</button>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card reveal-card">
                <i class="fas fa-microchip"></i>
                <h3>Electronics Technology</h3>
                <p>Micro-controller programming, robotics, and telecommunication systems.</p>
                <button class="btn-sm-stylish">View Syllabus</button>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card reveal-card">
                <i class="fas fa-snowflake"></i>
                <h3>RAC Technology</h3>
                <p>Modern refrigeration systems and HVAC industrial climate control.</p>
                <button class="btn-sm-stylish">View Syllabus</button>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card reveal-card">
                <i class="fas fa-utensils"></i>
                <h3>Food Technology</h3>
                <p>Food chemistry, quality control, and industrial processing techniques.</p>
                <button class="btn-sm-stylish">View Syllabus</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
        <section class="panel footer-section" id="section5">
            <div class="vision-box reveal-scale">
                <h2>Our Vision 2030</h2>
                <p>"To be the leading center of technical innovation in Bangladesh."</p>
                <div class="contact-strip">
                    <p><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> Magura, Khulna Division, Bangladesh</p>
                    <p><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> +880 1XXX-XXXXXX</p>
                </div>
                <button class="btn-primary ripple-btn">Apply For Admission</button>
            </div>
        </section>
        
    </div>


    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/locomotive-scroll@3.5.4/dist/locomotive-scroll.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/about.js"></script>
</body>
</html>